parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Lack of Rear Underride Guards on Semi-Trailers
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The absence of rear underride guards on semi-trailers can cause severe injuries or fatalities in the event of a collision, as vehicles can underride the trailer and intrude into the passenger compartment.
